 Galvatron looked at the map of all the bases. "I feel we need to make an 
alliance on this planet with one of the waring factions. I saw two pred 
tribes and a maximal one. Rodimus Prime is here and he has something I need 
before we can leave this planet. The engines couldn't survive space flight. 
Quilldart cant repair them which means we'll need to borrow some parts. One 
of the factions was headed by a bot ironically named Megatron. You all know 
that any bot given that name is worth watching. With his help I believe we 
can make quick work of the Maximals as they call themselves now."

--part1_62.22507ab5.2a5dcc6d_boundary
